rows.label: qst500104_msg0001
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh?! Nice people
appear out of nowhere!

rows.label: qst500104_msg0002
rows.name:
Yamama come to Superbia to search
for rare tasty-tasty ingredients.

rows.label: qst500104_msg0003
rows.name:
Plan was to climb to head of Divine Beast
and hunt for tastys, but somehow
Yamama get lost.

rows.label: qst500104_msg0004
rows.name:
All food supplies run out, so Yamama
resort to eat wild Emperor Beetles.
Turns out, quite tasty-tasty!

rows.label: qst500104_msg0006
rows.name: Yamama need to know way out of here!

rows.label: qst500104_msg0007
rows.name:
...OK, Yamama understand.
Thank friends for help!

rows.label: qst500104_msg0008
rows.name:
Yamama not want to get lost again,
so head home to Avaritia now.

rows.label: qst500104_msg0009
rows.name:
Take lots of Emperor Beetles.
Should make good enough ingredient!

rows.label: qst500104_msg0010
rows.name:
Oh yes, Yamama have many other
siblings also looking for tasty-tasty
juice ingredients.

rows.label: qst500104_msg0011
rows.name:
If friends meet in travels, please be nice
to other brothersisterpons too!
